---
// Features component
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">
        Warum MOCOS?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Wir bieten Ihnen den besten Service und die günstigsten Preise für Ihr neues Smartphone.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Bis zu 50% sparen -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">Bis zu 50% sparen</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Profitieren Sie von unseren exklusiven Händlerkonditionen und sparen Sie richtig Geld beim Handykauf.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Professionelle Beratung -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">Professionelle Beratung</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Unsere Experten beraten Sie kompetent und finden das perfekte Smartphone für Ihre Bedürfnisse.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Sofort verfügbar -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-red rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">Sofort verfügbar</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Große Auswahl an Smartphones direkt vor Ort. Keine Wartezeiten, sofort mitnehmen.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 100% sicher -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">100% sicher</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Alle Geräte mit Garantie und Gewährleistung. Seriöse Abwicklung und sichere Zahlung.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Deutschlandweites Netzwerk -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">100+ Partner</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Deutschlandweites Netzwerk von über 100 Partnern für Service und Support in Ihrer Nähe.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Kostenlose Einrichtung -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark ml-4">Kostenlos einrichten</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Wir richten Ihr neues Smartphone kostenlos ein und übertragen Ihre Daten.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 